<subSubSection pageId="241" pageNumber="846" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="241.[1450,2658,1241,2180]" pageId="241" pageNumber="846">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1452,1790,1994,2023]" pageId="241" pageNumber="846">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Pocock’s New Guinea Highland Rat has a large distribution and presumably large overall population. More research is needed to fully understand its natural history and conservation threats.
</paragraph>
